node.text: Can’t wait any longer for the release of the #Invicta X @shaq collection? Well, neither could @shaq ! Join him on his mission to bring his collection front and center to you this Thursday at 10pmET on @shophq .

node.text:
*CLOSED* The all-new King Python strikes tomorrow! Want to win this watch before it debuts? Follow the steps below to enter the giveaway:
1. Follow @invictawatch and @shophq
2. Like this post
3. Tag 2 friends who need this watch in the comments

The contest will run through July 27, 6pm ET. The winner will be announced on our IG Stories and contacted via IG messenger.

Per Instagram rules, this promotion is in no way sponsored, administered, or associated with Instagram, Inc. By entering, entrants confirm that they are 13+ years of age, release Instagram of responsibility, and agree to Instagram’s terms of use.
